Like most large corporations, Google's businesses have drawn some [[Criticism of Google|controversy]], such as [[copyright]] disputes in its [[Google Book Search|book search project]], or [[censorship by Google]] of search results as it works with countries such as [[China]] (and to a lesser extent [[France]], [[Germany]]), which have laws requiring the company hide information from Google users in their country.
